activity:
Spent the first month breaking down their entire business into different blocks. Quickly discovered multiple factors I could make assumptions from that would significantly impact this project: 
(1) the owners I was working with had very limited technical knowledge, but desired to be highly involved, therefore a large amount of resources would be spent here; 
(2) there was no structured data to start with that will benefit the new application; 
 (3) They have an existing legacy manufacturing application that I would have to interact with, and that data was in no beneficial condition
